    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1913-07-10T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1913-07-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="1191"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1191">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/8021.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of the Navy</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Navy Department</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-07-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 10, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to forward herewith for the
                    information of the Department of State copy of a telegram dated the 9th instant
                    received from the Commander-in-Chief of the Pacific Fleet, at Guaymas, Mexico,
                    reporting on conditions in that vicinity.</p>
                <p>Sincerely yours,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">F. D. Roosevelt</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
                <frus:attachment>
                    <opener>
                        <seg rendition="#center">[Inclosure—Extract.]</seg>
                    </opener>
                    <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head"
                        >[Untitled]</head>
                    <opener>
                        <dateline rendition="#right">
                            <placeName>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">U. S. S. Pittsburg</hi>, <lb/>
                                <hi rend="italic">Guaymas, Mexico</hi>
                            </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-07-09">
                                <hi rend="italic">July 9, 1913</hi>
                            </date>.</dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>Defense Guaymas continues to be strengthened. Americans still on <hi
                            rend="italic">Glacier</hi>. Six hundred Chinese under protection <hi
                            rend="italic">Pittsburg</hi> in camp on small island in outer
                        harbor.</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Cowles</hi>.</signed>
                    </closer>
                </frus:attachment>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
